        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Source data for Figs. 2–4 are available online. The gene sequence for LuxSit-i has been deposited to GenBank under the accession number OP820699. See Supplementary Data for design models of LuxSit and LuxSit-i. Codon-optimized plasmids encoding LuxSit-i for bacterial and mammalian expression are available through Addgene. Source data are provided with this paper.",
