        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "The Rosetta macromolecular modelling suite (https://www.rosettacommons.org) is freely available to academic and non-commercial users. Commercial licences for the suite are available through the University of Washington Technology Transfer Office. The source code for RIF docking implementation is freely available at https://github.com/rifdock/rifdock. All relevant scripts and an accompanying Jupiter notebook for family-wide hallucination scaffold generation are available here: https://files.ipd.uw.edu/pub/luxSit/scaffold_generation.tar.gz. All generated scaffolds are available here: https://files.ipd.uw.edu/pub/luxSit/scaffolds.tar.gz. Computational design scripts for the luciferase libraries are available here: https://files.ipd.uw.edu/pub/luxSit/luciferase_designs_methods.zip.",
            "block_bbox": [
