        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Competing interests A.H.-W.Y., C.N., Y.K., D.T., S.J.P., I.A. and D.B. are co-inventors in several provisional patent applications (application numbers 63/300171, 63/300178, 63/381922 and 63/381924 submitted by the University of Washington) covering the de novo luciferases and protein scaffolds described in this Article. A.H.-W.Y., C.N., J.Z. and D.B. are stockholders of Monod Bio, a company that aims to develop the inventions described in this manuscript. The remaining authors declare no competing interests.",
